    "body": "Due to an internal bug regarding the handling of scalars (ndim must be 0) in numpy prior to 1.15.0, openPMD-api will require the latest numpy 1.15+.\r\n\r\nSince there is a small regression with datetime pickling in 1.15.0 from the required fix and spack only packages 1.15.1 currently, we depend on 1.15.1 in the recipe.",
